cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and relation extraction. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses graph LSTMs for relation extraction. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with extracting knowledge from text, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks for relation extraction.
